# 弹幕系统 Verify Skill

验证整个系统的端到端工作流：
1. 启动服务（go run . &）
2. 注册用户 → JWT
3. 创建房间 → 开始直播
4. HTTP 发送弹幕
5. WebSocket 连接并接收广播
6. 验证历史查询
7. 关闭服务

## 流程

```go
// 启动
go run . &
sleep 3

// 注册用户
curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{"username":"verify","password":"verify123","nickname":"验证员"}' \
  | python3 -m json.tool

// 登录获取 token
TOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{"username":"verify","password":"verify123"}' \
  | python3 -c "import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin)['token'])")

// 创建房间
ROOM_ID=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -d '{"title":"验证房间"}' \
  | python3 -c "import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin)['id'])")

// 开始直播
curl -s -X POST "http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/$ROOM_ID/start" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN"

// 发弹幕
curl -s -X POST "http://localhost:8080/api/room/$ROOM_ID/danmaku" \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -d '{"content":"验证消息"}'

// 查历史
curl -s "http://localhost:8080/api/room/$ROOM_ID/danmaku"

// 停止
kill %1 2>/dev/null; wait 2>/dev/null
```

## 健康检查点
- `/healthz` → 200, `status: ok`
- `/readyz` → 200, 依赖状态
- `/metrics` → Prometheus 指标
- WebSocket 连接 → 能收到广播
